  "analyst_note": "CVE-2024-21888 (privilege escalation) and CVE-2024-21893 (SSRF/pre-auth RCE via SAML component) in Ivanti Connect Secure and Ivanti Policy Secure. Second wave of critical Ivanti vulnerabilities disclosed January 31, 2024. CVE-2024-21893 allows pre-authentication RCE via the SAML component \u2014 CISA mandated factory reset and upgrade for all affected devices. If Ivanti indicators are present in the response, treat as critical. Apply the Ivanti Integrity Checker Tool (ICT) and escalate for immediate patching.",
